      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HEATHCOTE RUPEE (1) rocketed out of the inside draw with a strong early sectional and gave a sight but had to settle for a placing, finishing second (19.62) at this track over 350m. Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Key chance in this line up. KARACHI (8) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame last run (19.52) at this track. Form here at the trip sound including six wins. Expected to feature again. AUSSIE SUPREME (3) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 1.5 lengths at this track in a handy 19.75 beating Fire Up Mark. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Capable of going well again. WILD VENUS (2) placed last time out so worth considering.",
